fancy Harvard medical school degree

09:52.553 --> 09:54.385
is a mountain of debt.

09:54.395 --> 09:57.046
Now, let's meet your first patient.

09:57.047 --> 09:58.960
This is Dobroslav.

09:58.970 --> 10:00.853
