guy's kind, polite, eager to help.

11:32.964 --> 11:35.796
For two days, he runs every test
in the book.

11:35.797 --> 11:38.677
And then he calls you and says it's
gonna set you back a thousand bucks.

11:38.687 --> 11:40.992
